Bontq,is,a,site,bug,tracking,and,issue,tracking,service,that,is,hosted,in,the,cloud,Bontq,can,also,be,used,as,a,project,management,platform,The,Bontq,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,Bontq,functionality,and,content,into,to,other,services,and,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,lists,of,users,issues,companies,and,more,adding,and,deleting,items,and,retrieving,files